</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-143_ pf-text-1">Research indicates that the proper use of tourniquets improves survival rates in severe limb traumas by as much as 85%.














</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-145_ pf-text-1">Studies reveal that prompt first aid response can reduce recovery time and decrease the likelihood of permanent injury or severe health outcomes.
















